Record Class DiffTreeLineGraphImportOptions

public record DiffTreeLineGraphImportOptions(GraphFormat graphFormat, DiffTreeLabelFormat treeFormat, DiffNodeLabelFormat nodeFormat, EdgeLabelFormat edgeFormat) extends Record
Options necessary for importing a line graph. This records contains information for importing a DiffTree from a line graph, such as the graph format and tree and node layouts.
